  <entry>
    <title>pip成功import失败why</title>
    <url>/2022/04/26/002_pip%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9Fimport%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5why/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>pip成功，import失败是比较郁闷的一件事。<br>1.检查python的安装路径，一般是tensorflow框架下的路径冲突问题</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> sys</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;sys.executable&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>2.在对应的路径下pip install对应的模块</p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>障碍</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
